01/04/2005
BUCHAREST, Romania -- A tape has been broadcast on the Arabic channel Al Jazeera, showing the three Romanian journalists taken hostage in Iraq, local media reported Friday (1 April).
The tape shows the three, together with a fourth person, appealing for help.
The United States confirms that an American citizen was taken with the three Romanians on Monday.
(Rompres, Romania Libera - 01/04/05)
